Flock Simulation Using Particle Swarm Optimization

Homepage:
    http://code.google.com/p/mycodeplayground/

Author:
    Xueqiao Xu <xueqiaoxu@gmail.com>

Description:
    This is a simple simulation of flock using the Particle 
    Swarm Optimization. The birds(red particles) will try to 
    follow your mouse. 
    If you want to know how the algorithm works, please refer to 
    http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Particle_swarm_optimization
   
Dependencies:
    Python 2.5+
    Pygame (http://pygame.org/download.shtml)
